Thank you.

00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:17.879
This is the corner room, right?

00:00:17.879 --> 00:00:22.440
So we have to, everyone leaves and comes at weird times.

00:00:22.440 --> 00:00:27.959
If you're here for doing, learning about list columns and data table, you're in the right

00:00:27.959 --> 00:00:28.959
place.

00:00:28.959 --> 00:00:34.880
Or maybe you wanted to see Julie's and Allison's beautiful artwork.

00:00:34.880 --> 00:00:37.020
You're also in the right place.

00:00:37.020 --> 00:00:39.919
Maybe you just heard that I had a few data table hex stickers.

